  🔧 To connect frontend:
  1. Update tesla_alerts_final.html to use API endpoints
  2. Replace localStorage functions with fetch calls to this server
  
  📝 Example API usage:
  GET  http://localhost:3000/api/reports          # Get all reports
  POST http://localhost:3000/api/reports          # Create new report
  GET  http://localhost:3000/api/reports/:id      # Get specific report
  DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reports/:id    # Delete report
  GET  http://localhost:3000/api/stats            # Get statistics
  
  Press Ctrl+C to stop the server
  
